7a0a&_nc_ohc=ez9MMar8iEAQ7kNvgFftgU7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAPjM133K9dJ1IJN4G65heqm7szw2l25uwSX2F243W3gw&oe=66CC6D5D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "cover.png", "id": "1691892224915749", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75580056_1691892228249082_8993988736869608245_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=U1Q7w0h1OXgQ7kNvgGm3k-J&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBVAk74yV0uHvjhxk1dSIV_ElKZbS37-xSznRPRxAUG7w&oe=66CC6EDA"}, "display_name": "Stealthy Swipers", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Description:\nImmerse yourself in the thrilling world of \"Stealthy Swipers,\" a cutting-edge VR game where your mission is to \"borrow\" valuable items from a vast, high-tech environment while evading detection by the colossal room owner. This game combines intense stealth mechanics, strategic gameplay, and a rich, futuristic setting to deliver an unforgettable virtual reality experience.\n\nGame Features:\n\n    Immersive VR Environment:\n        Experience a meticulously crafted, enormous space brought to life with state-of-the-art VR graphics. The game environment is designed to be visually stunning and deeply immersive, making you feel like you are truly inside a high-tech, futuristic world.\n\n    Stealth and Strategy Gameplay:\n        Engage in challenging stealth gameplay that requires careful planning and quick reflexes. Utilize shadows, create diversions, and use high-tech gadgets to avoid being detected by the vigilant room owner.", "short_description": "Description:\nImmerse yourself in the thrilling world of \"Stealthy Swipers,\" a cutting-edge VR game where your mission is to \"borrow\" valuable items from a vast, high-tech environment while evading detection by the colossal room owner. This game combines intense stealth mechanics, strategic gameplay, and a rich, futuristic setting to deliver an unforgettable virtual reality experience."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_priv